Ju Dou;;1990;;PG-13;;Drama,Romance;;7.7;;Yimou Zhang,Fengliang Yang;;Gong Li,Wei Li,Baotian Li,Zhang Yi,Ji-an Zheng,Ma Chong,Zhijun Cong,Wu Fa,Zhaoji Jia,Jia Jin,Xingli Niu,Qianbin Yang;;A woman married to the brutal and infertile owner of a dye mill in rural China conceives a boy with her husband's nephew but is forced to raise her son as her husband's heir without revealing his parentage in this circular tragedy. This tale of romantic and familial love in the face of unbreakable tradition is more universal than its setting.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099902/